## Conclusion — RED for the existing page:
 (1) The existing page documents [files.<name>] with fields that do not exist.
 (2) Even the structurally-correct [storage.<name>] HashMap is parsed by
     RuntimeConfig — a struct the binary does not load.
 (3) Storage routes are gated on .with_storage(backend) at
     server/builder.rs:L583-L588 and the binary never calls it.
     This is the same library-API gap as FW-3 #330 (TenantRegistry wiring).
